 text-sm sm:text-base\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin w-4 h-4 sm:w-5 sm:h-5 text-secondary-600\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><span>Itinéraire</span></a></div></div></div></div><main class=\"min-h-screen pt-16 lg:pt-20\"><div class=\"bg-background-100 border-b border-neutral-200 py-4\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors text-sm\" href=\"/\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-left w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"m12 19-7-7 7-7\"></path><path d=\"M19 12H5\"></path></svg>Retour à l&#x27;accueil</a></div></div><section class=\"bg-background-50 py-16\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto\"><h1 class=\"font-serif text-display-lg text-neutral-900 mb-4\">Contact &amp; Accès</h1><p class=\"text-body-lg text-neutral-600\">Réservez votre table ou contactez-nous pour une privatisation</p></div></div></section><section id=\"reservation\" class=\"py-section bg-background-100 bg-pattern\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><p class=\"text-primary-600 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-3\">Réservation</p><h2 class=\"font-serif text-display-md text-neutral-900 mb-4\">Réservez votre table</h2><p class=\"text-neutral-600\">Pour garantir votre place, nous vous recommandons de réserver, especially le week-end.</p></div><div class=\"bg-background-50 rounded-card shadow-warm p-8 lg:p-12\"><form class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div><label for=\"name\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900 mb-2\">Nom complet *</label><input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 outline-none transition-colors\" placeholder=\"Jean Dupont\" name=\"name\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"email\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900 mb-2\">Email *</label><input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 outline-none transition-colors\" placeholder=\"jean@email.com\" name=\"email\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"phone\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900 mb-2\">Téléphone *</label><input type=\"tel\" id=\"phone\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 outline-none transition-colors\" placeholder=\"06 12 34 56 78\" name=\"phone\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"date\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900 mb-2\">Date souhaitée *</label><input type=\"date\" id=\"date\" required=\"\" min=\"2026-03-26\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 outline-none transition-colors\" name=\"date\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"guests\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900 mb-2\">Nombre de personnes *</label><select id=\"guests\" name=\"guests\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 outline-none transition-colors\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"\">Sélectionnez</option><option value=\"1\">1 personne</option><option value=\"2\">2 personnes</option><option value=\"3\">3 personnes</option><option value=\"4\">4 personnes</option><option value=\"5\">5 personnes</option><option value=\"6\">6 personnes</option><option value=\"7-10\">7-10 personnes</option><option value=\"10+\">Plus de 10 personnes</option></select></div><div><label for=\"type\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900 mb-2\">Type de demande</label><select id=\"type\" name=\"type\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 outline-none transition-colors\"><option value=\"reservation\" selected=\"\">Réservation</option><option value=\"privatisation\">Privatisation</option><option value=\"traiteur\">Traiteur</option><option value=\"autre\">Autre demande</option></select></div></div><div><label for=\"message\" class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900 mb-2\">Message (optionnel)</label><textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-neutral-300 focus:border-primary-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500/20 outline-none transition-colors resize-none\" placeholder=\"Anniversaire, régime alimentaire, demande spéciale...\"></textarea></div><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-semibold rounded-button transition-all duration-300 focus-visible:outline-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary-500 to-secondary-600 text-white hover:from-secondary-600 hover:to-secondary-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98] px-8 py-4 text-body-lg w-full\" type=\"submit\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-send w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M14.536 21.686a.5.5 0 0 0 .937-.024l6.5-19a.496.496 0 0 0-.635-.635l-19 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.024.937l7.93 3.18a2 2 0 0 1 1.112 1.11z\"></path><path d=\"m21.854 2.147-10.94 10.939\"></path></svg>Envoyer la demande</button><p class=\"text-sm text-neutral-600 text-center\">Vous recevrez une confirmation par email sous 24h.</p></form></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-background-50 py-section\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16\"><div><h3 class=\"font-serif text-heading-xl text-neutral-900 mb-8\">Informations pratiques</h3><div class=\"mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-50 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin w-6 h-6 text-primary-600\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-1\">Adresse</h4><address class=\"not-italic text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed\">123 Rue de Paris<br/>92300 Levallois-Perret</address><a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/CsKc6rc471n63fV86\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block mt-2 text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium text-sm\">Obtenir l&#x27;itinéraire →</a></div></div></div><div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-50 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock w-6 h-6 text-primary-600\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\