2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z\"></path></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-1\">Téléphone</h4><a href=\"tel:+33123456789\" class=\"text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors text-lg\">01 23 45 67 89</a></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-secondary-50 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail w-6 h-6 text-secondary-600\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"16\" x=\"2\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7\"></path></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-1\">Email</h4><a href=\"mailto:contact@caracas-bar-tapas.fr\" class=\"text-neutral-600 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors\">contact@caracas-bar-tapas.fr</a></div></div><div class=\"pt-4\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3\">Suivez-nous</h4><div class=\"flex gap-3\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/caracasbartapas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-background-100 text-neutral-900 font-medium hover:bg-primary-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\">Instagram</a><a href=\"https://facebook.com/caracasbartapas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-background-100 text-neutral-900 font-medium hover:bg-primary-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\">Facebook</a></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><div class=\"aspect-video w-full rounded-card bg-background-100 flex items-center justify-center\"><a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/CsKc6rc471n63fV86\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-background-50 rounded-card shadow-soft hover:shadow-medium transition-shadow\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/200